âœ… 6. Topic: @Input() and One-Way Binding
ğŸ’¬ Interviewer Asks:
â€œWhat if the parent changes a value passed via @Input() â€” will the child automatically get updated?â€

âœ… Answer:
Yes, @Input() supports one-way binding from parent â†’ child.
If parent updates the value, child will reflect it automatically.

ğŸ”§ Code Snippet:
// parent.component.html
