ğŸ”¥ Angular Beginner Interview Q&A â€” Set 3

âœ… 1. Topic: NgModel & FormsModule
ğŸ’¬ Interviewer Asks:
"Youâ€™ve used [(ngModel)] in your template, but it's not working â€” no binding happens. What could be wrong?"

âœ… Answer:
You likely forgot to import FormsModule in your module.
ngModel is part of the FormsModule, not included by default.

ğŸ”§ Fix in app.module.ts:
