  this.router.navigate(['/about']);
}

âœ… 5. Topic: Basic Error Handling in Templates
ğŸ’¬ Interviewer Asks:
"How do you safely access nested properties in templates?"

âœ… Answer:
Use the safe navigation operator ?. to prevent errors when accessing undefined or null values.

ğŸ”§ Code Snippet:
<p>{{ user?.profile?.name }}</p>
If user or profile is undefined, it wonâ€™t throw an error â€” it just renders nothing.

